{"tid":319283,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"衛蘭被網友嫌棄　李亞男留言力撐","createTime":"2017-07-12T16:17:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-14T20:07:35.000Z","uid":22869,"like":34,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1088fcac4ecfb3f67759dec15342f314b46d08ff","tid":319283,"uid":22869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T16:17:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">衛蘭被網友嫌棄　李亞男留言力撐</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/13/001455_4b8286eb032d7c8994296c8d8e3e6866.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F13%2F001455_4b8286eb032d7c8994296c8d8e3e6866.jpg&h=83718d37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n藝人王君馨（Grace）同老公Daniel尋日（11日）喺美國會補辦婚宴，好友李亞男都係姊妹之一，佢今晚就上載一張同新娘子及一班姊妹包括岑麗香、苟芸慧、衛蘭等嘅合照上社交網，留言話：「Congrates again to my beautiful sister Grace and bro Danny! （再次恭喜我美麗的姊妹Grace同兄弟Danny）We are Soon to be called the #amazinghotwifegroup」<br />\n<br />\n但一班網民錯晒重點，係咁留言問姊妹之一嘅鍾嘉欣去咗邊？仲有網民話覺得衛蘭太肥，唔應該做Grace姊妹，搞到亞男忍唔住留言回覆呢位網民，話無論衛蘭高矮肥瘦都好，喺神眼中都係靚嘅。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">JANICE</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/13/001552_01b4662c93729b955f156a83664bc568.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F13%2F001552_01b4662c93729b955f156a83664bc568.jpg&h=284f2c96&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 